---
config:
  look: handDrawn
  theme: neutral
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor U as Usuario
  participant H as Home (React Native)
  participant T as Transferencias (Android)
  participant B as Backend mock

  U->>H: Tap "Transferir"
  H->>T: Abre pantalla nativa
  U->>T: Ingresa destinatario + monto
  T->>B: Enviar transferencia

  alt Transferencia exitosa
    B-->>T: OK + nuevo saldo
    T-->>U: "¡Transferencia exitosa!"
    T->>H: Notifica nuevo saldo
    H-->>U: Actualiza saldo
  else Saldo insuficiente
    B-->>T: Error
    T-->>U: "Saldo insuficiente"
  end
